This library uses WebKit style for indentation and format.
It is advisable to auto-format your code before you check-in any changes.

First install clang-format if you don't already have it:
$ sudo apt-get install clang-format

You can use clang-format utility with WebKit syle option:
$ clang-format -i -style=WebKit src/*

You can apply clang-format to a single file or a folder..
